      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but i already talk to my doctor and they're super busy, like i can't really get an appointment before my exams start next week. and like i said, it's just a natural herb, right? it's not like a heavy pharmaceutical. do you really think a little extra st johns wort would actually do something as serious as \"toxicity\"? it seems a bit extreme for just a supplement.",
